author_ssm: Marcia Bienfield and University Archives staff in 1979. Additional processing by Aleksandr Gelfand in 2013.
abstract_ssm: The collections contains the papers of Samuel Macauley Jackson (1851-1912) and The American Society of Church History (1888-1896) of which he was the secretary and treasurer for the eight years of its existance. It contains mostly correspondence between Jackson and other church leaders as well as a scrapbook of items and publications.
